import { MDBRow, MDBCol, MDBContainer } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';
import Movie from './movie';

const movieGrid = () => {
    return (
        <MDBContainer>
            <MDBRow className="col-12 rows-col-xxl-2 g-3 m-0">
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <Movie />
                </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>
        </MDBContainer>
    );
};

export default movieGrid;
